---
/**
 * Vista embebida desde Shopify (application_url). Estética alineada con la landing principal.
 */
import LandingLayout from '../../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';

const shopRaw = Astro.url.searchParams.get('shop') || '';
const shop = shopRaw.replace(/^https?:\/\//, '').replace(/\/+$/, '').toLowerCase();
const origin = Astro.url.origin;
const panelLogin = `${origin}/login?next=${encodeURIComponent('/configuracion')}`;
const panelDirect = `${origin}/configuracion`;
---

<LandingLayout
  title="Wazapp para Shopify"
  description="Conecta tu tienda Shopify con Wazapp: catálogo sincronizado y chat en tu vitrina."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-white font-professional antialiased text-app-ink overflow-x-hidden">
    <!-- Fondo suave (misma familia visual que el hero de la landing) -->
    <div class="pointer-events-none fixed inset-0 -z-10" aria-hidden="true">
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[min(100vw,900px)] h-[520px] rounded-full bg-brand-500/[0.055] blur-[100px]"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 translate-x-1/4 w-[480px] h-[480px] rounded-full bg-emerald-500/[0.06] blur-[90px]"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <header
      class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-app-line/80 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-white/70"
    >
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 h-[4.25rem] flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <a
          href={`${origin}/`}
          target="_top"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2.5 shrink-0 group"
        >
          <img
            src="/logo.png"
            alt=""
            class="h-10 w-10 rounded-xl ring-1 ring-app-line shadow-sm"
            width="40"
            height="40"
          />
          <span class="font-semibold text-app-ink tracking-tight text-[15px] group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors"
            >Wazapp</span
          >
        </a>
        <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3">
          <a
            href={`${origin}/contacto`}
            target="_top"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hidden sm:inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-app-muted hover:text-app-ink px-3 py-2 rounded-xl transition-colors"
          >
            Ayuda
          </a>
          <a
            href={`${origin}/`}
            target="_top"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-sm font-medium text-app-muted hover:text-app-ink px-3 py-2 rounded-xl transition-colors"
          >
            Web
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-14 sm:pt-20 pb-20 sm:pb-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 pl-3 pr-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-app-line bg-white/90 shadow-sm mb-8"
        >
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 relative" aria-hidden="true">
            <span
              class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75"
            ></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-emerald-500"></span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-[13px] text-app-muted font-medium tracking-wide">App conectada · Shopify</span>
        </div>

        <h1
          class="text-[2.1rem] sm:text-[2.75rem] lg:text-[3.25rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.06] text-app-ink"
        >
          Tu tienda, lista para
          <span class="block text-gradient-brand mt-1.5 pb-0.5">vender por chat</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-app-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Sincroniza productos con tu panel, activa el chat en la vitrina y atiende desde el mismo lugar que WhatsApp.
          Todo sin complicaciones: entra a Wazapp y sigue los pasos.
        </p>
      </div>

      {
        shop ? (
          <div class="mt-8 max-w-xl">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-app-line bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-brand-50/40 px-4 py-3.5 sm:px-5 shadow-sm">
              <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-app-muted mb-1">Tienda detectada</p>
              <p class="font-mono text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-app-ink font-medium tracking-tight break-all">{shop}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ) : null
      }

      <div class="mt-14 lg:mt-16 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-start">
        <!-- Pasos -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-5">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-600">Pasos rápidos</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <article
              class="group relative rounded-[22px] border border-app-line bg-white p-5 sm:p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-brand-500/20 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div
                  class="shrink-0 w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-brand-600"
                >
                  1
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-app-ink tracking-tight mb-1">Entra al panel</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm text-app-muted leading-relaxed">
                    Abre Wazapp en una pestaña completa (el botón hace eso por ti). Inicia sesión o crea cuenta.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article
              class="group relative rounded-[22px] border border-app-line bg-white p-5 sm:p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-brand-500/20 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div
                  class="shrink-0 w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-brand-600"
                >
                  2
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-app-ink tracking-tight mb-1">Vincula Shopify</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm text-app-muted leading-relaxed">
                    En <strong class="text-app-ink font-medium">Configuración</strong> →{' '}
                    <strong class="text-app-ink font-medium">Integración Shopify</strong> indica tu dominio{' '}
                    <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-app-ink">.myshopify.com</span> y conecta.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article
              class="group relative rounded-[22px] border border-app-line bg-white p-5 sm:p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-brand-500/20 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div
                  class="shrink-0 w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-emerald-700"
                >
                  3
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-app-ink tracking-tight mb-1">Sincroniza y activa el chat</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm text-app-muted leading-relaxed">
                    Sincroniza productos al CRM. Luego activa el chat en el diseño de tu tienda cuando te lo indiquemos.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 pt-4">
            <a
              href={panelLogin}
              target="_top"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl bg-brand-500 text-white font-semibold text-[15px] hover:bg-brand-600 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/25"
            >
              Ir al panel de Wazapp
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a
              href={panelDirect}
              target="_top"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-app-line bg-white text-app-ink font-semibold text-[15px] hover:bg-app-field/80 transition-colors"
            >
              Ya tengo sesión
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta decorativa (preview estilo producto + chat) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-28">
          <div class="relative">
            <div
              class="absolute -inset-px rounded-[26px] bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-400/25 via-transparent to-emerald-500/15 opacity-80"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="relative rounded-[25px] border border-app-line bg-white shadow-xl shadow-black/[0.06] overflow-hidden"
            >
              <div class="px-5 pt-5 pb-4 border-b border-app-line/80 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-50/50 to-white">
                <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-app-muted">Vista previa</p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-app-ink mt-0.5">Chat en tu tienda</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-5 space-y-3">
                <div class="flex justify-end">
                  <div
                    class="max-w-[85%] rounded-2xl rounded-tr-md bg-brand-500 text-white text-[13px] px-3.5 py-2.5 shadow-sm"
                  >
                    ¿Tienen este modelo en stock?
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-start">
                  <div
                    class="max-w-[90%] rounded-2xl rounded-tl-md border border-app-line bg-app-field/80 text-app-ink text-[13px] px-3.5 py-2.5 leading-snug"
                  >
                    Sí, está disponible. Te paso el precio y si quieres te ayudo con el pedido.
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-end">
                  <div
                    class="max-w-[70%] rounded-2xl rounded-tr-md bg-brand-500/12 border border-brand-200/60 text-app-ink text-[13px] px-3.5 py-2"
                  >
                    Perfecto, gracias
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="px-5 py-3.5 bg-app-field/50 border-t border-app-line/60 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <p class="text-[12px] text-app-muted">Bot y catálogo enlazados a tu Shopify</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-16 sm:mt-20 text-center text-sm text-app-muted max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        ¿Primera vez en Wazapp?
        <a href={`${origin}/`} target="_top" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-semibold text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-500"
          >Conoce planes y funciones</a
        >
        en la web principal. Esta página solo aparece al abrir la app desde Shopify.
      </p>
    </main>
  </div>
</LandingLayout>
